# Licensing for this distribution

This repository is a mixed-license distribution.  No single license applies to
every file.

- The historical SPHEREPACK Fortran implementation and derivative files are
  distributed under the UCAR/NCAR SPHEREPACK license in
  `LICENSES/UCAR-SPHEREPACK.txt`.  The original `LICENSE.spherepack` file is
  retained unchanged for provenance.
- The historical Python binding carries the permission and warranty notice
  preserved in `LICENSES/PYSPHARM-LEGACY-PYTHON.txt`.
- New files created specifically for the maintained `pyspharm-ng` project are
  licensed under the BSD 3-Clause License in `LICENSES/BSD-3-Clause.txt`,
  unless a file states otherwise.

The `NOTICE` file identifies material provenance and the conditions that must
be retained in source and binary distributions.  In particular, this project
must not imply endorsement by UCAR, NCAR, their sponsors, or contributors.
